	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This is the description I had planned to use for <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=33&amp;t=16993" class="postlink">Star Evil</a> in the multicart.<br /><blockquote style="margin-left: 1%; padding-left: 1%; border-left: 3px solid #555577;">
Your craft has crashed!<br />Now explore the wreckage<br />of the world you once knew.<br /><br />+ Move<br />ⒶⒷ ???<br /><br />Inspired by a game by<br />  Active Enterprises
</blockquote><br />I'm treating the entire A52-inspired part of the game as the opening cut scene because that's what it is.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
